These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, card-games, board-games, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Hobby   | board-games | card-games | puzzles | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, tiparillo, baccarat, dunhill
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere between the tiparillo-smoker and the fonseca-smoker##7
3. the baccarat-smoker is between the tiparillo-smoker and the dunhill-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar   | fonseca | dunhill | baccarat | tiparillo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
